Class WToken

java.lang.Object
us.mn.state.dot.tms.utils.wysiwyg.WToken
Direct Known Subclasses:
Wt_IrisToken, Wt_Rectangle, WtCharSpacing, WtColorBackground, WtColorForeground, WtFeedMsg, WtFont, WtGraphic, WtJustLine, WtJustPage, WtLocator, WtNewLine, WtNewPage, WtPageBackground, WtPageTime, WtStandby, WtTextChar, WtUnsupportedTag
public abstract class WToken extends Object
WToken - WYSIWYG-Editor Token An object holding WYSIWYG information about a MULTI tag or individual text character. This object includes the string representation of the token, the 0-based coordinates of the token on a page, and any errors detected by the error detection code.
Author:
John L. Stanley - SRF Consulting, Gordon Parikh - SRF Consulting
